# NeoBank Super-App — Implementation Plan

A full-stack banking super-app built in Java (Spring Boot) with a modern frontend.
PayFlow (P2P wallet) and ClearLedger (expense tracking) are embedded as child modules.

---

## Architecture Overview

```
NeoBank (Parent)
├── 🔐 Auth Module          → Login, Signup, JWT, Roles
├── 👤 User Module          → Profile, KYC, Settings
├── 🏦 Core Banking Module  → Accounts, Balances, Statements
├── 💳 Transactions Module  → Deposits, Withdrawals, Transfers
├── 💸 PayFlow Module       → P2P Payments, Requests, QR
└── 📊 ClearLedger Module   → Expenses, Budgets, Invoices
```

We'll build this as a **modular monolith** — one Spring Boot app with clean internal module boundaries.
Later, each module can be extracted into its own microservice if needed.

